mysql> SELECT B.mem_id, M.mem_name, B.prod_name, M.addr, 
    ->         CONCAT(M.phone1, M.phone2) AS '연락처' 
    ->    FROM buy B
    ->      INNER JOIN member M
    ->      ON B.mem_id = M.mem_id;
+--------+--------------+--------------+--------+-------------+
| mem_id | mem_name     | prod_name    | addr   | 연락처      |
