mysql> SELECT A.emp "직원" , B.emp "직속상관", B.phone "직속상관연락처"
    ->    FROM emp_table A
    ->       INNER JOIN emp_table B
    ->          ON A.manager = B.emp
    ->    WHERE A.emp = '경리부장';
+--------------+--------------+-----------------------+
| 직원         | 직속상관     | 직속상관연락처        |
+--------------+--------------+-----------------------+
| 경리부장     | 관리이사     | 2222                  |
+--------------+--------------+-----------------------+
1 row in set (0.00 sec)

